                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280110-178-off935 t18280110-178-cd936"></join>, 21 lbs. weight of lead, value 2s., the goods of the 
                     <persName id="t18280110-178-victim1103" type="victimName">
                        <rs id="t18280110-178-viclabel937" type="occupation">St. Katherine Dock Company</rs>
