               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280110-178-person1104">
                  THOMAS 
                  FOGG
               <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1104" type="surname" value="FOGG"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1104" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1104" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I saw the prisoner walking down Rosemary-lane, on the 7th of January, with a bag - I went up to him, and asked what he had got, he said, Nothing - I took hold of it, and found it was lead; he then said he found it close to St. Katherine Docks. I took it to my brother, who found where it came from.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280110-178-person1105">
                  JAMES 
                  FOGG
               <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1105" type="surname" value="FOGG"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1105" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1105" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I received the prisoner, and this lead from my brother - I went and found it had come from the gutter of a house, which is to be pulled down.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280110-178-person1106">
                  WILLIAM 
                  SITGROVE
               <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1106" type="surname" value="SITGROVE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1106" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1106" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am in the employ of the St. Katherine Dock Company. I have fitted this lead on the top of a house, belonging to them - it fits exactly.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18280110-178-person1107">
                  THOMAS 
                  COULSBY
               <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1107" type="surname" value="COULSBY"></interp>
