                     <interp inst="t18280110-178-person1107" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I know the prisoner has slept in the stable of the house from whence the lead was taken; it belongs to the Dock Company.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. I was going towards Sun-yard - I saw a bag, and took it up, and what should it be but lead.</p>
